---
const facts = [
  { icon: '📍', label: 'Würzburg' },
  { icon: '📚', label: '4. Semester E-Commerce' },
  { icon: '💡', label: 'JESUS 1ST' },
];
---

<section
  id="ueber"
  class="py-24 md:py-32"
  style="background: #110E1C;"
  aria-labelledby="ueber-headline"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- ─── Left: Decorative ────────────────────────────────── -->
      <div class="fade-up">
        <div
          class="relative aspect-square max-w-[420px] mx-auto rounded-2xl overflow-hidden"
          style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #061108 0%, #0C0A14 100%); border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);"
        >
          <!-- Big JM monogram -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span
              class="font-headline text-[12rem] leading-none select-none"
              style="color: rgba(201,168,76,0.06);"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              JM
            </span>
          </div>
          <!-- Overlay card content -->
          <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-end p-8">
            <blockquote class="text-white/80 text-lg italic leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-accent-primary pl-4">
              „Christus in euch, die Hoffnung der Herrlichkeit."
            </blockquote>
            <cite class="text-accent-light text-sm mt-3 not-italic tracking-widest">Kolosser 1,27</cite>
          </div>
          <!-- Corner accent -->
          <div
            class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 rounded-bl-full"
            style="background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(201,168,76,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);"
            aria-hidden="true"
          ></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ─── Right: Text ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <div>
        <!-- Section label -->
        <div class="fade-up mb-4">
          <span class="text-accent-primary text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">Über mich</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Headline -->
        <h2
          id="ueber-headline"
          class="font-headline text-[clamp(3rem,7vw,5rem)] leading-none text-white fade-up"
          style="transition-delay: 0.05s;"
        >
          WER<br />
          <span class="text-accent-primary">ICH BIN</span>
        </h2>

        <!-- Body text -->
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed fade-up" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
          <p>
            Ich bin Jakob — Student, Marketer, Creator und Christ. Ich lebe in der Schnittstelle zwischen digitalem Business und echtem Leben: Ich lerne jeden Tag dazu, probiere aus, mache Fehler und wachse.
          </p>
          <p>
            Mein Antrieb? Kolosser 1,27 — Christus in mir, die Hoffnung der Herrlichkeit. Was das konkret bedeutet, siehst du in allem, was ich tue.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Quick facts -->
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3 fade-up" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
          {facts.map((fact) => (
            <span
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium"
              style="background: rgba(201,168,76,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2); color: #E8C87A;"
            >
              <span aria-hidden="true">{fact.icon}</span>
              {fact.label}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>

        <!-- Stats row -->
        <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 fade-up" style="transition-delay: 0.25s;">
          {[
            { value: '4.', label: 'Semester' },
            { value: '2+', label: 'Jahre Erfahrung' },
            { value: '∞', label: 'Motivation' },
          ].map((stat) => (
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="font-headline text-4xl text-accent-primary">{stat.value}</div>
              <div class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-1">{stat.label}</div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
